      <title>印尼总统普拉博沃向特朗普示好，与美国高层会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/indonesia-s-prabowo-courts-trump-meets-top-executives-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚总统普拉博沃·苏比安托周日与唐纳德·特朗普通电话表示祝贺，并可能于本周与这位当选总统亲自会面，以寻求与新政府建立联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/indonesia-s-prabowo-courts-trump-meets-top-executives-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 04:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国电信运营商达成 5.6 亿美元英超联赛协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/thai-telecom-carrier-strikes-560-million-english-football-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国电信运营商 Jasmine International Pcl 同意支付高达 5.6 亿美元的价格购买英超联赛的转播权，以吸引客户使用其流媒体业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/thai-telecom-carrier-strikes-560-million-english-football-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 03:35:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vista Equity 募资主管 Greg Myers 离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/vista-equity-s-fundraising-head-greg-myers-departs-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Vista Equity Partners 的投资者开发和筹款活动主管已离开这家收购公司，这是 Vista 做出的“战略决定”，此举将使其领导层更贴近投资者群体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/vista-equity-s-fundraising-head-greg-myers-departs-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 03:30:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国计划削减购房税以刺激财政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/china-plans-to-slash-homebuying-taxes-in-fiscal-stimulus-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国政府正计划削减购房税，加大财政支持力度，以重振低迷的房地产市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/china-plans-to-slash-homebuying-taxes-in-fiscal-stimulus-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 01:46:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国锌业表示仍在审查 18 亿美元股票出售计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/korea-zinc-silent-on-share-sale-as-quarterly-profit-drops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国锌业公司周二表示，该公司仍在考虑是否继续推进存在争议的 18 亿美元股票出售计划，但将考虑监管机构和其自身投资者提出的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/korea-zinc-silent-on-share-sale-as-quarterly-profit-drops</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 00:20:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私募股权投资的监狱健康公司 Wellpath 宣布破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/pe-backed-prison-health-care-firm-wellpath-declares-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Wellpath Holdings Inc. 是美国最大的监狱医疗服务提供商之一，由于无法履行债务并面临高昂的劳动力成本而申请破产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/pe-backed-prison-health-care-firm-wellpath-declares-bankruptcy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 00:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧和美元下跌导致油价两周来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-12</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国需求前景疲软、美元走强以及市场担心市场可能转向供应过剩，油价出现两周来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-12</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 23:28:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡特朗普议程，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡当选总统唐纳德·特朗普可能采取的行动以及美元走强对地区经济的影响，大多数亚洲股市下跌。彭博美元指数回升至一年来的最高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 22:36:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普当选总统引发市场关注，美国国债收益率小幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bond-investors-set-up-for-jump-in-yields-with-focus-on-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者希望重新点燃上周唐纳德·特朗普赢得总统大选后引发的抛售浪潮，美国国债开盘走弱。]]></description>
